&lt;h2 id="symbol-search-符号查询">Symbol Search 符号查询&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>使用默认的搜索框，哪怕设置了 Filter，&lt;br>
还是会给出一大堆的无关选项。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;img src="https://moyf.github.io/hugo-stack-blog/hugo-stack-blog/p/rider-%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%A4%E5%88%99%E5%B0%8F%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/Assets/20231218_161622_233_copy.png"
width="898"
height="196"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="458"
data-flex-basis="1099px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>这个时候就应该用 &lt;code>Alt+\&lt;/code> 来查找函数啥的：&lt;br>
&lt;img src="https://moyf.github.io/hugo-stack-blog/hugo-stack-blog/p/rider-%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%A4%E5%88%99%E5%B0%8F%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/Assets/Pasted-image-20231218161730.png"
width="695"
height="111"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="626"
data-flex-basis="1502px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>这个是限定范围的，&lt;br>
好用很多！&lt;/p>
&lt;h2 id="fast-surround-快速包裹">Fast Surround 快速包裹&lt;/h2>
&lt;p>有时候会经常需要把比如 &lt;code>UAkSwitchValue&lt;/code> 转成 &lt;code>TStrongObjectPtr&amp;lt;UAkSwitchValue&amp;gt;&lt;/code>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>这时候可以用 &lt;a class="link" href="https://www.jetbrains.com/help/rider/Templates__Applying_Templates__Creating_Source_Code_Using_Live_Templates.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
>Live Template&lt;/a> 功能：&lt;br>
&lt;img src="https://moyf.github.io/hugo-stack-blog/hugo-stack-blog/p/rider-%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%A4%E5%88%99%E5%B0%8F%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/Assets/Pasted-image-20231218161946.png"
width="984"
height="701"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="140"
data-flex-basis="336px"
>&lt;/p>
&lt;p>&lt;code>$SELECTION$&lt;/code> 代表选中的文本，&lt;br>
&lt;code>$END$&lt;/code> 代表插入之后的结尾放哪儿。&lt;/p>
&lt;p>注意右边有个 &lt;code>Mnemonic&lt;/code> 速记符，是在这个时候用的：&lt;br>
&lt;img src="https://moyf.github.io/hugo-stack-blog/hugo-stack-blog/p/rider-%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%A4%E5%88%99%E5%B0%8F%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/Assets/Pasted-image-20231218201007.png"
width="302"
height="199"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="151"
data-flex-basis="364px"
>&lt;br>
唤出的方法：&lt;br>
&lt;img src="https://moyf.github.io/hugo-stack-blog/hugo-stack-blog/p/rider-%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%A4%E5%88%99%E5%B0%8F%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/Assets/Pasted-image-20231218201038.png"
width="898"
height="247"
loading="lazy"
class="gallery-image"
data-flex-grow="363"
data-flex-basis="872px"
>&lt;br>
可以用快捷键 &lt;code>Ctrl+E, U&lt;/code> 来快速唤出。&lt;/p>
&lt;hr>
&lt;p>在右键的 Contextural Menu 可以显示，但这样太麻烦了。&lt;br>
&lt;img src="https://moyf.github.io/hugo-stack-blog/hugo-stack-blog/p/rider-%E7%9A%84%E4%B8%A4%E5%88%99%E5%B0%8F%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86/Assets/Pasted-image-20231218162128.png"
